title: Star Citizen and more
author: VD
content_html: Tonight’s Brainstorm with Derek Smart is open to everyone. Is Star Citizen on track, in trouble, or something altogether else? If you’d like to get in on it, over 100 of the 500 seats are still available. You can register here.
